Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.90,0:00:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You like him...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.69,0:00:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and he likes you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.03,0:00:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.41,0:00:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.04,0:00:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can promise you one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.05,0:00:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.26,0:00:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...make you cry, Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.95,0:01:04.83,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Usotsuki na anata nakimushi no atashi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.83,0:01:10.80,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Doushite umaku ikanai wa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.80,0:01:16.93,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Oshare shita kami mo rain suton no tsume mo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.93,0:01:22.89,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Anata wa kidzuki mo shinai ne
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.89,0:01:30.27,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Love kanashii namida nanka ja nai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.27,0:01:34.99,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Me ga kawaite hirihiri suru dake
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.99,0:01:40.91,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kono unmei bakari I love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.83,0:01:49.79,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimi dake wo atashi dake wo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.79,0:01:54.71,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Atsui omoi wo uketomete
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.92,0:02:01.85,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Doko made mo tsunagattetai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.85,0:02:08.60,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawaikunai nakigao mo se mo aishiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.95,0:01:04.83,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't things go well between
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.83,0:01:10.80,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,the liar, you, and the crybaby, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.80,0:01:16.93,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't notice my styled hair
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.93,0:01:22.89,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,or my nice set of press-on nails.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.89,0:01:30.27,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Love isn't about the unhappy tears that go along with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.27,0:01:34.99,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Those tears only leave my eyes dry and hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.99,0:01:40.91,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,I love this destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.83,0:01:49.79,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,between only you and only me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.79,0:01:54.71,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to accept your hot feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.92,0:02:01.85,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,and be taken by you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.85,0:02:08.60,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite your uncute, tearful face and your shortness, I still love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.95,0:02:24.08,Episode title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(900,1100)\fscx113.75\fscy103\pos(159,377)}Episode 22 ...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.41,0:02:24.16,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for walking me home...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.49,0:02:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all. You should warm yourself up inside, and go to bed early.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.21,0:02:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.02,0:02:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.57,0:03:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just at the station, and you weren't there...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.78,0:03:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for breaking our promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.29,0:03:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go home...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.73,0:03:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Head inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.75,0:03:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't think something like this would make her cry, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.76,0:04:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You thought something like this was nothing, since you didn't have feelings for Yamamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.47,0:04:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you were able to go, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.10,0:04:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because there'd be nothing to feel guilty about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.56,0:04:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's different for Takahashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.86,0:04:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you plan to explain your actions to Takahashi, who's still not confident about all of this yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.28,0:04:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and Takahashi experience things totally differently, all the way down to the bottom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.00,0:04:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't intend to blame you for going to see Yamamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.09,0:04:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.47,0:04:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think the important thing to do is always the same as the right thing to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.97,0:04:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it important to not hurt Takahashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.32,0:06:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't think something like this would make her cry, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.12,0:06:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You thought something like this was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.71,0:06:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's different for Takahashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.30,0:06:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You hurt Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.44,0:07:01.19,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2\fscx317.5\fscy263.75\b1\c&H63626C&\frz19.911\pos(244,390)\frx356\fry26}Training\NSchool
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.02,0:07:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.96,0:07:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.35,0:07:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You catch a cold or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.68,0:07:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your face is bright red.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.68,0:07:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It took me two hours to walk home last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.02,0:07:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! In that snow storm?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.86,0:07:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't have enough for the bus...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.36,0:07:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...because the taxi ride was too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.82,0:07:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go rest somewhere... you look like you're about to collapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.57,0:07:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congrats!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.37,0:07:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.75,0:08:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana, so you're finally...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.58,0:08:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.54,0:08:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were so worried for you, like we were your parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.75,0:08:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.42,0:08:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did everything go well?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.59,0:08:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.94,0:08:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.31,0:08:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... I have to get the class day book...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.56,0:08:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.99,0:08:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.86,0:08:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.81,0:09:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.65,0:09:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Takeuchi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.48,0:09:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard he fell?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.44,0:09:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yeah. He went home early.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.28,0:09:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously? Did he have a fever?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.95,0:09:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.00,0:09:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said it was just a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.83,0:09:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.29,0:09:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.46,0:09:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you... avoiding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.26,0:09:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.02,0:09:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He stood you up and went to see Yamamoto instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.19,0:09:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with that? He's scum!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana, you're just being selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.94,0:09:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? He went to see another girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.53,0:09:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that awful?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.57,0:10:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not like he hid it. He told her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.66,0:10:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When accidents like that happen, you can't do anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.00,0:10:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't fully understand the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.96,0:10:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know about that! Why does Nana have to be the one to wait, and not Yamamoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.13,0:10:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because she's his girlfriend, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.71,0:10:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Always expecting him to put you first because of that is a bit much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.34,0:10:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's trust in the relationship, something like that shouldn't bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.89,0:10:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trust, you say? It's because he goes and does things like this that she can't trust him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.10,0:10:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not really his problem, is it? It's hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.69,0:10:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My... problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.73,0:10:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano probably went because he didn't think there would be a problem, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.03,0:10:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he trusted you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.57,0:10:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.87,0:10:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trust...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.24,0:10:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... if my mom collapsed, I don't think Yano would come running to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.91,0:10:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't even call Yano, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.25,0:10:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that kind of sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.30,0:10:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd come to you, Mizu-chin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.42,0:11:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'd come, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.56,0:11:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trust, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.11,0:11:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's something I always seem to be lacking...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.28,0:11:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like we kept hitting on the same point every time...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.74,0:11:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamamoto and I had sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.79,0:11:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deep in my heart, I may not have been able to forgive that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.38,0:11:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.39,0:11:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...may really be with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.19,0:12:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But please... don't make me any more uneasy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.68,0:12:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.80,0:12:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your fever seems to have broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.10,0:12:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You slept for almost a day, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.73,0:12:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there's someone here to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.19,0:12:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I let her in?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.44,0:12:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's here to see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.57,0:12:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, stay in bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.75,0:12:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.33,0:12:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you almost had pneumonia?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.00,0:12:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.88,0:12:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.29,0:13:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.38,0:13:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was worried, since you took two days off from school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.34,0:13:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made a copy of the class notes for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.39,0:13:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all right. I can get them from someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.89,0:13:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sliced up the cantaloupe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.11,0:13:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She brought it as get-well-soon gift, Motoharu. Be sure to thank her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.20,0:13:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've loved you this whole time...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.59,0:13:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mom's really pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.63,0:13:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You might catch my cold, so go home when you're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.09,0:13:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hardly ever catch colds, so I should be fine---
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.59,0:13:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.74,0:14:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ended up coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.53,0:14:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really want to see him yet, but I got worried because he's been absent for two days...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.83,0:14:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll look in on him, and then leave--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.93,0:14:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.76,0:14:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamamoto-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.73,0:14:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's a bit selfish to say this, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.44,0:14:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I don't want you to see or call Yano anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.32,0:14:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.41,0:14:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because Yano's the guy I'm going out with.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.53,0:14:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't you tell him that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.75,0:14:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're Nana-san's little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.96,0:15:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're not just some stranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.84,0:15:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why Yano finds it hard to make a decision!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.21,0:15:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see him as "my sister's boyfriend".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.97,0:15:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you even know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.93,0:15:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've only been his girlfriend for a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.81,0:15:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've known him since before he was going out with my sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.48,0:15:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and after she died, when he was about to cry and ready to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.99,0:15:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know I can understand him a whole lot more than you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.00,0:15:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A whole lot more than you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.34,0:15:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do anything about that, can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.89,0:15:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do anything about what I don't know, can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.97,0:16:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or... am I the wrong one here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.19,0:16:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.98,0:16:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I not understand him enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.36,0:16:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She says she knew him when he was having the hardest time ever...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.95,0:16:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trying so hard, too... so very hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.99,0:16:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's still... not enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.33,0:16:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.58,0:16:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a limit to things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.42,0:16:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right to try your hardest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.67,0:16:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... really understanding him is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.35,0:16:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The same way he can't do what you want him to do, you can't understand what he wants you to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.19,0:16:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing you can do about the differences in the way you two think.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.92,0:17:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... what am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.59,0:17:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.60,0:17:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Are you alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.10,0:17:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I heard someone else. Were you talking to someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.10,0:17:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I was on my cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.36,0:17:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bother coming to visit. You'll catch my cold, so go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.24,0:17:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold out, so close your window.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.87,0:17:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.62,0:17:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take... I don't understand anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.08,0:17:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't understand what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.75,0:17:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How to go out with Takahashi without hurting her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.01,0:18:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it's just one of my defects as a human?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.39,0:18:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a first for you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.64,0:18:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.11,0:18:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.61,0:18:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must be really pathetic, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.20,0:18:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't forgive myself for making her cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.17,0:18:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... I'm not confident that I won't be able to keep from hurting her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.34,0:18:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.01,0:18:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I definitely don't want to give up on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.73,0:18:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.15,0:18:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.74,0:19:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.20,0:19:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... are you sure no one else really came?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.16,0:19:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.17,0:19:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Motoharu! You can't go outside like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.10,0:19:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Motoharu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.23,0:19:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.94,0:19:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.23,0:19:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Motoharu, look out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.32,0:19:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't see anyone, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.45,0:19:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just because your fever's dropped a little doesn't mean you can let your guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.46,0:20:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi! Wait--!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.43,0:20:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so nice to me when I'm weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.35,0:20:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're weak...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.71,0:20:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.09,0:20:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make your fun smile like usual, and be yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.72,0:20:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll be able to...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.64,0:20:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is useless...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.31,0:20:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you always have to cry?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.19,0:21:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd always make you smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.40,0:21:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you supposed to be happy with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.20,0:21:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.45,0:21:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.95,0:21:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why else would you stick with this relationship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.58,0:21:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd always find you before you had to go looking for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.37,0:21:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd do whatever you wish for!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.12,0:21:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one way to allow such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.80,0:21:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't figure it out, you don't have the right to do such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.97,0:21:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... can make you happier than he can.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.81,0:21:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I've been wanting to talk to you about, Motoharu...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.82,0:21:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.03,0:21:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's a little weird to tell you when you're like this, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.74,0:21:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you're not around very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.53,0:21:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thinking of getting divorced.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.33,0:22:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can make you happier than he can, Takahashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.34,0:22:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've actually been worrying over this for about a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.88,0:22:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wasn't able to make up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.84,0:22:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But about one month ago, one of my old friends gave me a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.22,0:22:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you remember her. You know, that lady who used to be my hair stylist?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.35,0:22:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't leave you like this anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.86,0:22:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And she asked if I could come help her with her work.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.69,0:22:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finding employment at my age was one of my big worries, so I thought this might be my chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.24,0:22:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I don't want to let it pass me by.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.91,0:22:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's put an end to all the crying and worrying.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.80,0:22:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When two people are together, aren't you supposed to have more fun than when you're alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.18,0:22:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we moving to Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.19,0:23:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to protect you, Takahashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.83,0:23:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every night before falling asleep, I wish for my dream to come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.88,0:23:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And each morning manages to be different.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.51,0:23:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I still can't see the future.
