Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.57,0:21:55.41,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,A silent rain falls.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.41,0:22:02.05,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,A slightly chilly rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.05,0:22:08.84,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,But it continues to fall, without actually hitting me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.84,0:22:15.85,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,as if it's trying to freeze my heart instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.85,0:22:22.65,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always found your gentle back
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.65,0:22:31.20,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,on any day, but where do my
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.20,0:22:35.04,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,winding feelings point?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.04,0:22:41.92,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what you see
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.92,0:22:49.68,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,before you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.68,0:22:56.02,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,We keep on running
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.02,0:23:03.44,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,and we seem like we're going to reach, but don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.44,0:23:06.24,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,At that distance away from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.16,0:23:19.00,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Rain will fall again someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.00,0:23:26.05,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,A slightly lonely rain
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.05,0:23:32.30,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,will pour all around and spread
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.30,0:23:39.94,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,as if it's meant to soothe my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.94,0:23:46.57,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always looking at your cute back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.57,0:23:54.70,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,but these winding feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.70,0:23:58.79,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,point me in the other direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.79,0:24:05.84,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I waiting for
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.84,0:24:13.05,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,at the end of my search?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.05,0:24:19.56,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,We keep on running
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.56,0:24:26.57,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,and we seem like we're going to catch up, but don't.
