Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.06,0:25:11.11,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,I might not be the\N right girl for Yano after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.11,0:25:15.11,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't understand\N his feelings at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.11,0:25:20.95,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't we do\N something so easy...?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.70,0:25:27.38,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I take back the\N words I said two years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.38,0:25:32.13,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,That was still the worst\N thing you could've done.
